Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘\N이 라이브를!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,모두가 훗날 자랑할 수 있을만한\N밴드가 되겠습니다!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,말 잘했다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,무도관에 가버려~!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,고―!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐시기 씨도\N멋졌다!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,줄도 끊어졌는데\N열심히 하더라!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,얼른, 고토 씨!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,한 마디 쯤은\N뭐라고 답해줘야지!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,어!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,아앗...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,아...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}커...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}커뮤 장애는 사전에 대본\N안 만들어두면 말을 못하는데...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}생각도 못한\N토스를 날리시면...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,아무거나\N재밌는 말...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,아무거나\N재밌는 말...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 아무거나....!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,아무거나...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,재밌는 거...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.80,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,10)\fna두리둥실\fs60\move(1215,635,1255,660,0,1620)}헤헤헿헿
