Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩 진짜 최고~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,인간적으로\N걱정 좀 해라!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,내 말이!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,들것 가져 와!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮니!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,우리 언니가 죄송해요~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,아아...!\N아니에요, 뭘요...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,푸흐흡~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}하아아아...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,2000)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}끝났..다...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨, 괜찮아?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,정신이 좀 들어?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,아...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,네
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,다행이다~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,막 크게 다친 건\N아닌가 봐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,저기...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,망쳐버려서...\N진짜 죄송해요...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,모처럼...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,아냐~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,왠지는 몰라도\N오히려 더 달아오른 거 같던데?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,어...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 아...\N니지카쨩네는요...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,지금은\N정리하고 계셔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨만 괜찮으면\N이 다음에 뒷풀이 가자는데
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.87,0:09:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,그래도 안 되겠으면\N다음 기회로 하고...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,맞다, 놀랐어요...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,응?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,키타 씨...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,어느샌가\N그렇게 잘 치셔서...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,반주뿐이지만...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord3\pos(824,912)}배킹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 저기...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,나는...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,남들을 사로잡을만한\N연주는 못해...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}그래도...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}모두와 맞추는 것만큼은\N잘하는 모양이니까...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,앞으로도 기타 더 열심히 할 테니까\N가르쳐줘야 해?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}고토 씨...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리쨩!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,어!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,에...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼\N먼저 가 있을게?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,준비 다 되면\N와야 해?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...
