Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:39.11,Default - A,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}종료하겠습니다
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,뒷풀이, 뒷풀이~♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩, 괜찮으려나~
