Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.24,Default - A,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fn태 나무\fs50\bord5\c&H090909&\3c&HBEBEBE&\frz343\frx350\fry0\pos(1835,580)}출입금지
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 다이빙했던\N사람이다
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,아~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,롹킹한 미친년\N걔구나
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,600)\fn양재백두체b\b0\fs80\bord6\fscy20\t(00,150,\fscy200)\t(150,250,\fscy80)\t(250,350,\fscy100)\pos(1190,490)}끄앍!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}언젠가...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}언젠가 고등학교\N진짜 때려치워버릴 거야...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,아버지\N죄송합비다...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,언니,\N뭐 하는 거야~?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,아빠한테 빌린 기타...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,라이브에서\N망가뜨려버렸어요...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,고..고개 들자!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,아빠는 하나도\N화 안 났으니까~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,응!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,페그가\N고장난 것뿐이지?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇게\N걱정 안 해도 돼~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,그래도...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,게다가 라이브 도중에\N부서먹다니~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,왠지 아빠는\N막 흥분되는데~!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,600)\fna두리둥실\b1\fs80\fs70\fscy20\t(00,150,\fscy200)\t(150,250,\fscy80)\t(250,350,\fscy100)\pos(935,560)}엩?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,요즘은 파괴전용 기타란 것도\N팔고 있다고 하니깐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,다음 라이브 때\N한 번 해주라~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}딸내미를 어떤 방향으로\N몰아가고 싶은 거야...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:41.05,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna두리둥실\fs60\pos(1082,238)}아빠~\N놀아줘잉~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:45.05,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,600)\fna두리둥실\fs50\pos(730,170)}빨리, 아빠아~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,이것도\N마침 좋은 기회니까~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리도 자기 기타를\N마련해보면 어때?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 그것도 괜찮겠다~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,이번처럼 문제가 생겼을 때\N바로 대응할 수도 있고 말야!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,아니...\N그래도...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,알바는 하고 있지만\N라이브 할당량 때문에 사라지니까
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,그럴 돈은...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,걱정 마!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs90}돈이라면 있다!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:56.02,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HCB&\fn양재백두체b\b0\fs90\bord6\fscx179.8\fscy179.8\pos(911.37,583.35)}따흡!?
