Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,초 슈퍼 봇치쨩...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,엉?\N알바가 뭐 어쨌다고?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,앝...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 어, 그...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:13:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐냐...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,앞으로도\N성심성의껏...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,시..심혈을 기울여\N일 열심히 하게쓤다...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,왜 갑자기\N결의표명을 한대??
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}알바를 관두는 건\N말 꺼내는 게 제일 힘들다구...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그냥 쨀까...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아, 아니아니!\N주소도 다 까발려졌는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그게 아니고!\N모두한테 민폐를...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘\N악기점에 갈 거랬지?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아무거나 점장님한테 헌상하면\N관두게 해줄지도!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}지금이라면\N돈도 잔뜩 있으니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:22.79,Default - A,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 저기...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,점장님이 지금 갖고 싶은 걸\N물어봐주시면 안 돼요...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩이\N그러던데...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,언니,\N곧 생일이기도 하니까
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,선물 하려는 걸까?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs90}딱히 없다!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,필요 없대~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,10)\fn양재백두체b\b0\fs50\fscy20\t(00,150,\fscy200)\t(150,250,\fscy80)\t(250,350,\fscy100)\pos(1040,155)}히약!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}끝났다...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,난 Dingwall이랑 Le Fay의\N신작 헤드리스
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,그리고 DARKGLASS의\N앰프 헤드가 갖고 싶어
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.84,Default - A,,0,0,0,,여러분~\N악기점에 가자구요~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:47.45,Default - A,,0,0,0,,렛츠라 고~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.92,Default - A,,0,0,0,,다녀오세요~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}봇치쨩, 넘 착하당...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,하지만 나는\N서프라이즈가 좋거든
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,응?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:54.91,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna하얀구름\b0\fs80\bord7\c&H817883&\3c&HEDF1EC&\frz14.28\frx18\fry356\pos(1250,255)}오챠노미즈역
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,악기점을 찾는다면\N역시 오챠노미즈지~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,있지, 히토리쨩!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}왜 이렇게\N악기점이 많은 걸까~?
